 SUMMARY OF RESPONSIBILITIES 
 Welcomes and greets visitors, applicants, clients, and associates. 
 Answers and routes any calls received through the main switchboard. 
 Supports the recruiting and employment process, initiates applicants participation in the online job application, pre-employment testing, and related screening tasks as directed. 
 May manage mail services, supply procurement, and provide a variety of administrative duties to support the site and the HR team. 
 
 POSITION QUALIFICATIONS 
 Demonstrated ability to greet all visitors in a positive, welcoming and courteous manner. 
 Ability to multitask and be attentive to detail while using basic working knowledge of general office equipment and administrative practices. 
 Efficient ways of routing/resolving specific calls and visitors. 
 Advanced knowledge/use of Microsoft Office programs (PowerPoint, Excel, Word), along with organizational and exceptional interpersonal and communication (verbal and written) skills. 
 Must be able to actively manage several functions/projects consecutively.
 Outgoing personality and ability to remain calm and professional in all situations is a must. 
 Quantity and maintenance of supply orders. 
 Organization of reception area. 
 Advise job applicants of the general process. 
 
 WORK EXPERIENCE 
 Six months or more experience in a reception, secretarial or administrative support position in a customer service environment. 
 Basic typing/computer skills required with knowledge of MS Office products preferred. 
 
 Education 
 High school diploma or equivalent. Sitel 6 days ago original job Report job Apply Now Apply On Company Site Save this job Save this job Administrative Coordinator jobs in Las Vegas, NV Jobs at Sitel in Las Vegas, NV Administrative Coordinator salaries in Las Vegas, NV Company Info Follow Get job updates from Sitel Sitel 11,611 reviews As a global leader in end-to-end customer experience (CX) products and solutions, Sitel GroupÂ® partners with the worldâ€™s best-loved brand... Let employers find you Thousands of employers search for candidates on Indeed Upload your resume Hiring Lab Career Advice Browse Jobs Browse Companies Salaries Find Certifications Indeed Events Work at Indeed Countries About Help Center Â© 2021 Indeed Do Not Sell My Personal Information Accessibility at Indeed Privacy Center Cookies Privacy Terms Let Employers Find You Upload Your Resume 
 
 
 
 
 
